HR Manager – Saudi National
The Gulf Recruitment Group
Location:
Riyadh, Riyadh Province
Date: 30-04-2014
Job Code:
LK 883295
Payrate: 25,000 To 25,000 (AED)
Job Type: Employee
Job Status: Full Time
Categories:
HR
The Gulf Recruitment Group
Saved!
Job Details
As the creator of some of the world’s most recognized brands this truly multinational giant is going from strength to strength in the KSA market.  With innovative products and consistent investment into new product development, there really is no limit to it’s success.
Requirements
An experienced and commercially focused HR Manager is required to manage the Saudi operations HR team and Factory, supporting the efficiency and development of the factory.  The role manages a full HR remit covering all aspects from recruitment, training, performance management, to comp & bens, policy and procedure improvements.  There will many challenges in this position including a key focus on employee engagement and ongoing Saudization.
This position requires a strong individual with a solid HR background and good understanding of the KSA market.
The successful candidate will have  minimum of 5 years HR experience gained in a factory ideally within the FMCG sector.
You MUST be a Saudi National and possess excellent communication and negotiation skills with the ability to work well with senior managers.
